Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.13,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,On the night of Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:08.23,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I made up with Shiina,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:11.76,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and passed the "Let's Make \Na Game" proposal screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:18.07,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If things had gone well between \NJin-san and Misaki-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:20.58,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have been the \Nperfect Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:25.68,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:39.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.02,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:17.92,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,400)}#15 Where is My Usual Self?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiina, you remember \Nwhat I said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:19.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-sensei's going on vacation \Nto Australia over winter break,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:21.35,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can't stay in Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:22.61,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:25.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why haven't you asked \NRita to come get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:28.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You realize we're all going home, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama-san, don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:31.68,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My head's been full of other thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.38,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I completely forgot \Nabout going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:37.75,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Forgetting that is a huge problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:41.05,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go home anyway, so I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:41.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, what about you, Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:44.37,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:50.92,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My hometown's full of \Nmemories of me and Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:53.94,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:56.98,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:02.07,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you'll all have \Nto go stay at Kanda's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:02.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:04.18,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:06.80,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:10.15,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you're packed \Nand ready to leave by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.92,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, strike while the iron's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:15.59,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:21.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi, this is a bullet train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast, isn't it? Whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we found people to \Ntake care of the other six.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, only Komachi was left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:32.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it goes 285 kilometers \Nper hour! Zoom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.68,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Worrying about the past \Ndoesn't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to focus on the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.45,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's some backwards optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:43.95,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer bamboo shoots...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:50.96,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I gave my last bamboo shoot to Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.07,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I already ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:54.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You rushed to eat that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:59.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai, do you \Nwant some mushrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I like bamboo shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:03.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:06.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat all the mushrooms, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:10.84,Saku-main,ANNOUNCEMENT,0000,0000,0000,,We will shortly be arriving in Hakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:16.65,Saku-main,ANNOUNCEMENT,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for using the \Nbullet train today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:25.66,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wh-Wh-What are all \Nthese people doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:31.42,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, th-thanks for letting \Nus stay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:34.94,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! I can't stay at a boy's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.58,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that after coming this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:39.55,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,And there're even more \Nsweet and fragile girls now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.51,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Kamiigusa Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.91,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.01,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,She's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:49.10,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Welcome, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:52.00,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the friends Sorata \Nmentioned on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.91,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,You're all such cute girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.91,Saku-overlap,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.35,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.63,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be more fun that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:58.27,Sign,PAN,0000,0000,0000,,Successful Surprise!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.02,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's teasing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.74,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:05.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.08,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall allowing \Nyou to be polygamous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Not even the country's laws allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.18,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:20.21,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.86,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:25.09,Saku-overlap,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a fun end to the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:31.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand how you \Nadapted to life in Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.06,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Jin's had his dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.47,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you suddenly get an urge \Nto hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.60,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice of you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand my situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently in Fukuoka with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:55.45,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-chan told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:59.57,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I respect you. So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What happened between you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and Misaki-senpai on the \Nnight of Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.67,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I told Misaki I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.64,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I confessed my love to Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, why is Misaki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.85,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I asked for more time because I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:17.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:22.82,Sign,BOOK,0000,0000,0000,,College Entrance Examination Series
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:22.82,Sign,BOOK,0000,0000,0000,,Osaka Art Schools
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:22.31,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to college in \NOsaka to chase my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.28,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I love Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.70,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,No, exactly because \NI'm in love with Misaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:32.50,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't become a worthless \Nman who's abandoned his goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:38.29,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I want to move forward for once, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:41.17,Sign,PITCH,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's Make a Game" \NRhythm Battler Vol. 1 \NRhythm Action Battle Game \NEntry No. 06848860 \NKanda Sorata
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.46,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.37,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Misaki for me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:49.01,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She'll get jealous if I talk to you \Nfor too long, so I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you at one of your \Ngirlfriends' homes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.60,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I broke up with them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.30,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying with my friend, \Nthe Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.30,Saku-overlap,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Who are you calling your "friend"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.10,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:01.81,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.90,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Student Council President...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.45,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}former{\i0} Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:08.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:10.15,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.26,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.99,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But you're also equally right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.02,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:20.61,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, \NI'll make dinner every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:21.56,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Every night?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.28,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.54,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.87,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Motsunabe, chanpon, mentaiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's a real Hakata dinner right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:31.72,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:34.47,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Sorata found himself a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.18,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.93,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think I could \Nbe Kanda-kun's bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.93,Saku-overlap,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What are you doing, Onii-chan? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.58,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, do you want a wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:44.90,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to defeat me before \Nyou can marry my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:47.86,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you're too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:50.51,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't defeat Yuko like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:51.61,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't accept her challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.22,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.07,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I have to get into Suimei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.87,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and face Mashiro-san \Nin an all-out battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I will have to use my Plan C on Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No annihilating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:04.46,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,But, Yuko, your father is opposed to \Nyou taking the Suimei entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.04,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I know! That's why I need \NOnii-chan to convince—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:07.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.81,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Instant rejection?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:11.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Convince him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy during the break \Npreparing for my presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.26,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Presentation? What's that? \NDoes it taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.22,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.68,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you take \Nthe Suimei entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.35,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely will {\i1}not{\i0} allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.37,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,That's final.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.07,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:31.69,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.22,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to start studying \Ntogether tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:35.74,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:41.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If your father sees you studying hard, \Nhe might change his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.12,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do, Onii-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.31,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san's such a good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.70,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally the one I need \Nto keep my eye on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.76,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin! Did you finish writing the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.50,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.97,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thanks, Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:09.68,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll start working \Non some layouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:10.27,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:21.85,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:28.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I shouldn't just \Nfocus on giving the presentation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.96,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but also put myself in the \Nshoes of the listener...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:35.30,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,Presentation Techniques Lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:35.30,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,Grab the attention of your listener!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:31.51,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.43,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's important \Nto include information...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.30,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the screening committee \Nwill find interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Maid-chan, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:42.24,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,If you're truly grateful, why don't \Nyou take a quick trip to England...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.65,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and take care of someone for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I don't do those kinds of jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.56,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to hearing the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the results of \Nthe presentation, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:55.65,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,Genre: Rhythm Action Game
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Something interesting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Now I just have to figure \Nout what that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:06.33,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Game \NPitch Contents \NFun \NTarget \NConcept \NBenefits
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:06.33,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Something the listener \Nwill find interesting? \NHow to play \NSystem \NControls \NAppeal of the product?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:02.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've written all the necessary \Npoints in my pitch document.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What else would the screening \Ncommittee want to hear about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.04,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, help me study!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.70,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,She went shopping with Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:15.35,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,So, while she's gone, teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of books...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:19.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This magazine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:22.35,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about reading \Nit over my break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:25.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You came here planning to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:27.32,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,This is my oasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:30.44,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,A manga I like is serialized in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.92,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's written by someone called \NShiina Mashiro-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.49,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,The art's really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:37.29,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but there are some \Nweird characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.39,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,These two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:43.20,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Those are based on Jin-san \Nand Misaki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.10,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Their expressions of emotion \Nleave something to be desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.57,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,They won't get together, \Nbut they won't break up either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.58,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what they \Nreally want? No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.16,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:52.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:56.38,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think of it, Mashiro-san, \Nyou've got the same name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:59.48,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}her{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:00.05,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:00.96,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.46,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a huge fan! \NCan I have your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That was a major change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.54,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko-chan, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.40,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you wait. \NLet's work hard together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:10.22,Saku-overlap,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mashiro-sensei, I'm cheering for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:12.80,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to next month's volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:17.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, are you \Ngoing to meet your deadline?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:20.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to use a \Ncomputer over the break...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:21.60,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I already did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it to Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:26.09,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I injured my finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.08,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I did it after it healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:31.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:32.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.50,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you like about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:35.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:39.27,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I've liked that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.06,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.22,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:58.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is this for my presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.11,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Use your abilities by hitting the\N buttons in time with the rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.11,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Use combos to score lots of points!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:02.86,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stop liking me if I \Ndraw things that aren't manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:06.83,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes my pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:22.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.60,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.36,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You've become a truly competent man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.22,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's gotten a lot \Neasier to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.78,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you've grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:33.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so cool! I want to hear it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:39.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, did you make these? \NI thought Mom did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She used to make them \Nfor me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:45.14,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, she taught me. Are they good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:45.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They're great, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.49,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:53.86,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're so focused on your work, \Nyou don't even eat dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:56.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's already New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:59.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The presentation's right after the break,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:02.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it took a while for it to take shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But I still feel a little uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, if you were on \Nthe screening committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.47,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,what would you want to hear \Nduring a presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:15.14,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about games, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.02,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If I worked for a company,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:20.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I might wonder if a game \Nwould make money or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. That might be obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was so caught up in \Nwhether it'd be fun or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had completely forgotten about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:31.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! Thanks, Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:36.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're always helping me out, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:40.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You made me rice balls for my \Nfirst presentation, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And you've got an audition coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:49.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:51.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.02,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:57.60,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, doing other things \Ntakes my mind off of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:02.90,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I can do until the script \Narrives is prepare myself mentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:04.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.24,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:12.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Once my script gets here, I'll get you \Nto help me practice for my audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:13.40,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:17.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd help you in any way I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:23.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, because I want you \Nto pass your audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:28.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching you work hard\Nsince we were first years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:30.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:37.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is, I might just \Nactually want you to prove...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:40.35,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,hard work is always rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I shouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.90,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.12,Saku-main,NAMAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.08,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.47,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to work hard with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, you always work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think so, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:10.22,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There have been lots of things \NI don't understand lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.29,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.82,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of things \NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.45,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:38.36,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki, how do you want \Nthings to go with Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what you want? "No, no."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.96,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:46.06,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,In my manga, you're together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.80,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.28,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:57.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:16:04.75,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,If I were hurting Jin by making \Nanimations, I'd stop animating...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:05.98,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:09.04,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Would Jin like you if you did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:15.63,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata likes that I love to draw manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:18.24,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What does Jin like about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.22,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have enough \Nchopsticks on that side?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.48,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:32.37,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen her study so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.74,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,But Dad opposes her applying to Suimei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:39.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you talked to Dad, \Nhe'd allow it in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.69,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,But Yuko asked you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Tell Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:49.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,that I need to talk to him \Nwhen he has a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.17,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:56.45,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Your noodles will get soggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:03.14,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I told Mom, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:05.57,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to convince Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.09,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Opportunity waits for no man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:12.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?! \NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.46,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,If you make excuses by \Nsaying you're not ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and let opportunities pass you by,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll never get another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:20.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Don't get so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.02,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to talk to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.59,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:27.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's why you came in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.23,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd waited until \NI got out of the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:33.14,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I need to teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.28,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,about life while I still \Nhave breath in my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.96,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Opportunity waits for no man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:39.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I got it already! \NI wanted to talk about Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be taking studying seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:46.12,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so can't you at least \Nlet her apply to Suimei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If she tries and fails, \NYuko will accept that, won't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:54.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if she ends up attending a school \Nhere, won't that put your mind at ease?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:58.26,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who are you talking to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.25,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please just die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.80,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,So, which girl are you serious about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't give up, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me questions\N like we're kids at a sleepover?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:10.86,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be so indecisive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:14.54,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember raising such a girly-ass son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Can you just stop now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.27,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,But it's your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:20.19,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Live it how you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.73,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,If you intend to go to college, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:25.12,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make enough money to pay \Nfor your and Yuko's tuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:27.43,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.52,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in Yuko's case, it's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:34.03,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,impossible for her to get into Suimei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.30,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.83,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,I stayed in too long, \Nand now I can't move. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:43.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:46.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize for making me think \Nyou were even a little cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.91,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably a mistake to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get into the bath drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.56,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.90,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,What man could talk \Nto his own son sober?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're the girly-ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:18:59.13,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:02.18,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:06.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in any mood to \Ncelebrate the new year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:14.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Staying up to watch the sunrise is a bit \Nover-the-top for a New Year's celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:17.17,Saku-main,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,And the man who suggested it passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.75,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What does Jin love about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:41.30,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, thanks for talking to Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:45.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded like he would have allowed \Nit even if I hadn't said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:48.21,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:50.04,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.42,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:58.56,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop animating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:00.30,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I just end up doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:06.50,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I want to go back to \NSakura Hall and make more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:11.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My head's full of thoughts of \Nbackground animations for this shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.65,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and original screen \Nsplashes of that character!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:17.23,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin said he liked that about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.86,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I like you the way you always are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:20.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,S-So do I!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:24.58,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I love myself, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:26.65,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you all worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:27.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:32.09,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make Jin's anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.46,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Using the script Jin wrote, \NI'll make an animation myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:37.84,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:41.55,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make Jin look at me this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make my presentation a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll pass my audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.19,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.59,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get into Suimei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:56.54,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Meatball beam, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use your special ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.32,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I like meatballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:03.90,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Jin gets accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's sprint \Ntowards the rising sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.04,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-san, there's a cliff over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.98,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's shout Geronimo and take the plunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:12.57,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:13.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A paratrooper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:13.87,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A superhero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:16.30,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,This girl's just plain weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:22.80,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The three days after Misaki-senpai's \Nrevival flew by...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:26.86,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And the day came for us \Nto return to Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:31.68,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, I'll be coming next \Nmonth for the entrance exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.11,Sign,LUNCH,0000,0000,0000,,Kashiwameshi Bento
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.11,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Our winter break's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:48.12,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Things are just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:55.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:00.52,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to face that nervousness again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:05.09,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, I'm even \Nlooking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:33.44,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:35.05,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's my job to make dinner.
